  <conbody>
    <note id="note_rhp_nkh_wyb" type="important">
      <p>Apply the <codeph>placement=break</codeph> attribute on the <codeph>image</codeph> element
        to make it fit the page width.</p>
      <p>The <codeph>scalefit=yes</codeph> attribute setting does the same, but figure title
        placement will be incorrect.</p>
      <p>Revert to using a manual <codeph>scale</codeph> attribute setting if the automatic approach
        does not work.</p>
    </note>
    <note id="note_hdg_pld_3fc" type="attention">Setting the <codeph>width</codeph> attribute is
      usually the best approach for changing figure size.</note>
  </conbody>
